channel.title: Is this right?!?
channel.description: Ok so i bought a vps to host my server from vpsland and, they took the money out sent me the regular stuff. i've waited 24 hours havent recieved the ip to log in, and when i try to log in it just tells me that i have no account when i go to forgot password it says my email is not reconized. Duno what i should do :/ any 1 wanna tell me pls?

item.title: Is this right?!?
item.dc:creator: @EzioAuditori EzioAuditori
item.description:
@EzioAuditori wrote:

Make sure you log-in with the correct credentials.
Most vps websites, when you make an account, are case-sensitive.
So make sure you use the EXACT email/account name you used to sign up with, and change all Capital letters, basically process of elimination till you get the correct log in name.
